				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Addendum:<BR>
When waiting for the Sarnak Crypt Raider to spawn be pretty careful.  The entire area where you should be waiting for him is between the round tower and the beach, and there isn&#8217;t really a safe area where nothing might walk by.  While there I saw sabertooths from tigresses down to kits, greater skeletons and greater scalebone skeletons, goblin warriors, and the occasional Iksar Bandit.  The Crypt Raider is significantly easier than most everything around.<BR>
Here&#8217;s a tip if you don&#8217;t already do it: When you&#8217;re meditating you can hit the F8 key to find out what the nearest NPC is.  As soon as you have something targeted that will agro on you, stand up and find out where it is.  I&#8217;ve never seen a sabertooth attack someone unprovoked.
